應一併繳納上訴審裁判費。\r\n中　　華　　民　　國　　110 　年　　8 　　月　　27　　日\r\n                          書記官  林政良","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/TNEV/110%2c%e5%8d%97%e7%b0%a1%2c964%2c20210827%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"TNEV,110,南簡,964,20210827,1","JYEAR":"110","JCASE":"南簡","JNO":"964","JDATE":"20210827","JTITLE":"清償債務"}